synopsis:      Convert to/from the ISO 8601 time format
description:
  Conversion functions between Haskell time types and the ISO 8601 format,
  which is often used for printing times, e.g. JavaScript's @new Date().toISOString()@.
  .
  CHANGELOG
  .
  Version 0.1.0
